{"tid":640557,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[錢照比 中國水域 香港冇權理] 人工島崩堤 施工圖首曝光 工程師質疑未解「隨機擺放」之謎","createTime":"2018-04-24T11:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T15:45:04.000Z","uid":51620,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"7582731a1b025b3263919842473ada09d6b2d18b","tid":640557,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T11:01:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180424/58109713\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180424%2F58109713&d=PIhFHYhkq2G3Nufb4QOKIYS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=d9321c52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180424%2F58109713&h=c8be2655\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180424/58109713</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180423/large/1524496599_1c5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180423%2Flarge%2F1524496599_1c5a.jpg&h=0c0d75db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港珠澳大橋東、西人工島被質疑防波堤崩塌，港府昨（23日）公開東人工島防波堤工程的施工圖，強調防波堤沒有出現「被沖散」的情況。不過，資深土木工程師倪學仁指圖中防波堤兩邊呈圓形（圖），與早前網民航拍照片所見的防波堤被沖散情況有明顯分別，認為施工圖仍未能解釋事件。<br />\n<br />\n運輸及房屋局昨向立法會提交文件，交代港珠澳大橋人工島防波堤事宜。港府公開東人工島防波堤工程的施工圖，包括東島結構平面佈置圖，以及東人工島島隧結合部平面圖。文件指綜合實地視察、查閱施工圖及照片記錄，路政署並無發現防波堤有移動迹象，更強調防波堤沒有出現「被沖散」的情況。當局又指東人工島（不包括與隧道結合部份）施工圖於2011年8月完成審批，承建商於2013年8月於東人工島與高架橋樑處開始安放扭工字塊，但不包括與沉管隧道結合位置。至於東人工島與隧道結合位置的施工圖則於2014年10月完成審批，其後未有再作設計更改，而該部份的扭工字塊於2016年沉管隧道安裝後才開始安放。<br />\n資深土木工程師倪學仁看了有關施工圖後，指圖中防波堤兩邊均呈圓形，與早前網民航拍照片所見的防波堤疑被沖散情況有明顯分別。他又稱，兩幅施工圖未能解釋防波堤看似被沖散、或扭工字塊隨機擺放的原因。<br />\n記者 譚靜雯"},{"pid":"69f272116c81e73a56a1ff38af227fc8dd1ab5e9","tid":640557,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:55:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喂 你叫人點拆"},{"pid":"562b4317a523d7da57f43119eae14477df5731b8","tid":640557,"uid":61462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T13:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"398b4bf0d640d4f09dc0e0f9001b3d7baa89cbd8","tid":640557,"uid":5499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T13:07:53.000Z","msg":"屌你，話左隨機放，你整張圖出黎，特首點解話呀"},{"pid":"360e82c69b30138e09e0ee16a7c417cfc949854f","tid":640557,"uid":171718,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"398b4bf0d640d4f09dc0e0f9001b3d7baa89cbd8","tid":640557,"uid":5499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T13:07:53.000Z","msg":"屌你，話左隨機放，你整張圖出黎，特首點解話呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T13:10:34.000Z","msg":"施工圖只是建議 實際擺放base on situation<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"882b77e37d086f0b30f0fba5e94b353991c1000f","tid":640557,"uid":62950,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"360e82c69b30138e09e0ee16a7c417cfc949854f","tid":640557,"uid":171718,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"398b4bf0d640d4f09dc0e0f9001b3d7baa89cbd8","tid":640557,"uid":5499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T13:07:53.000Z","msg":"屌你，話左隨機放，你整張圖出黎，特首點解話呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T13:10:34.000Z","msg":"施工圖只是建議 實際擺放base on situation<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T13:11:41.000Z","msg":"施工圖只是劃定範圍 實際擺放係隨機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ac0ca25c3d8311467ca08470095e1c8fe